ygData.messageBody:
Hi,
I am new on this list and also new to the necromancer world. What beings
will kill us on site? I am an erudite and would like to go to Qeynos but
not sure if I will be killed, as I was in palace in front of wizard guild.
Also , where is the guild in Qeynos and what weapons and/or armor should I
be getting and are there any quests that necros can do?
Any answers would be helpful or maybe a web site for necros.
Thank You,
Salmissra, 4th circle, Karana
----- Original Message -----
From: Ort-Man <ortman@...>
To: <EQ_Necromancer@onelist.com>
Sent: Tuesday, June 01, 1999 7:16 AM
Subject: [EQ_Necromancer] Factions


> From: Ort-Man <ortman@...>
>
>
> Since killing Crushbone Orc's isn't advisable for a Dark Elf necro, are

> Zelrek, Rallos Zek
